cs.SY, cs.DS, cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the abstraction of large-scale linear consensus networks, which involves topics related to control systems (cs.SY), distributed systems (cs.DS), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.NE). The paper specifically focuses on the performance bounds of the abstracted network, which is a key concern in control systems. Therefore, cs.SY is the most likely sub-category. The paper also deals with optimization algorithms, which are commonly used in machine learning and optimization (cs.LG, cs.MA). Finally, the paper deals with distributed systems, which is a key concern in cs.DS.
